Your Speaker as an NFT

...And exclusive perks!
15% discount on next year sponsoring for PBWS 2023 or Paris NFT Day 2023
Collaborate in the making of next edition conference programme. Choose the thematic of one session.
Get priority placement at the event
Get 2 exclusive webinars and their marketing campaign on our platform after the event
